*local*						*sync*

- 'options'					[same]
+ data

-'username'					-'blockID' [2 chars] [0-9]?[a-z]|[A-Z]|[0-9]
+ blockID [2 chars]			+ "username"
+ encounters [4 bytes]		+ separator
+ tags(ID) [10x 1 byte]		+ encounters [4 bytes]
+ separator					+ tags(ID) [10x 1 byte]     // local separator here is used to support other tag lengths
							+ ...


- 'tagID'					[same]
+ enabled [1 byte]
+ frequency [4 bytes]
+ name + sep
+ symbol + sep
+ NR_ALIASES
+ alias + sep + alias + ...
+ NR_COLORS
+ color [4 byte] + ...

- 'storage-update-info'		[same]
+ '<KEY><username>?'                    // key can be blockID -> if blockID username follows
+ TIMESTAMP
+ '<KEY><username>?'
+ ...

- 'block-meta-info'			[none - this can be constructed from the blocks]
+ "username"
+ blockID


[MISC]
Lichess usernames:
+ At least 2 chars
+ Must start with a letter
+ Maximum length is 20


